WEBVTT

00:00.870 --> 00:03.939
SIDNEY: There is a war raging inside us.

00:04.858 --> 00:08.995
A war between the spirit and the flesh.

00:09.939 --> 00:11.859
We all feel that battle...

00:12.948 --> 00:18.983
..that pull between our
desires and our duties.

00:23.059 --> 00:25.605
But your inequities have separated

00:25.631 --> 00:27.374
between you and your God,

00:27.930 --> 00:30.255
and your sins have
hid His face from you,

00:31.188 --> 00:32.800
that He will not hear.

00:35.483 --> 00:37.203
If we are to be looked on by God,

00:37.662 --> 00:39.335
to be loved by Him,

00:40.335 --> 00:43.646
we must turn our back on temptation.

00:46.435 --> 00:49.040
Temptation is the source
of all suffering.

00:54.560 --> 00:56.919
AMANDA: Temptation is
the source of all suffering?

00:57.444 --> 00:59.267
Honestly, Sidney...

01:00.146 --> 01:01.706
What are we doing?

01:03.182 --> 01:04.601
What am I doing?

01:05.900 --> 01:10.083
If God is love, and making love is love,

01:10.652 --> 01:13.482
then what's so terribly wrong?
That's what I've never understood.

01:20.268 --> 01:23.070
Sorry. Sorry. I'm...

01:24.979 --> 01:26.325
Leonard!

01:26.680 --> 01:28.320
Leonard, I can explain!

01:28.360 --> 01:30.193
You tell me I'm lying to myself.

01:30.979 --> 01:32.960
You're the one who is lying!

